#Campaign
Here lie the ruins of [bold][_text256_54_]Ascefilia[reset], the might city.
Do you see the crumbling towers?

It is said that its people still dwell here, as ghosts and demons, evil creatures. The villagers claim that these are the things that torment them.
[_text256_134_][bold]Hollows[reset] is what they are...

Do you wish to explore it? This God forsaken place?